---
description: Core stack and file conventions
alwaysApply: true
---
- Use Next.js App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4
- Use `cn()` from `lib/utils.ts` for all class names
- Use the shared `Icon` wrapper from `components/ui/icon.tsx`, never raw Lucide icons
- Use `getSupabaseBrowserClient()` from `lib/supabase/client.ts`
- Shared utilities go in `lib/`
- Reusable UI components go in `components/ui/`
- Documentation goes in `docs/`
- Never hardcode API keys or credentials — always use environment variables
- Never commit `.env.local`